org.jruyi.system

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jruyi.system.Constants

  • public final class Constants
extends Object

    Defines standard names for the JRuyi framework properties.

    The values associated with these keys are of type java.lang.String, unless otherwise indicated.
